{"title":"西财摄记｜Stay with me","uid":"b57a1197cee8d27e8121f563ab62bd02","slug":"推文11","date":"2021-10-25T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:59:41.901Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文11.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235244320.png","content":"<p>“See ya never gone my way</p>\n<p>Better will someday”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235517773.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235517773\"></p>\n<p>我们见一面吧</p>\n<p>在冬天，在下雪天</p>\n<p>在我们最浪漫的年纪里</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235527337.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235527337\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235533420.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235533420\"></p>\n<p>他出现在飘落的初雪里</p>\n<p>因为她的召唤</p>\n<p>因为她在等待</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235542079.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235542079\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235546928.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235546928\"></p>\n<p>所以会在寒冬有了樱花飘落和22℃的灿烂阳光</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235558778.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235558778\"></p>\n<p>他会站在芥麦花田里拿着一束花等待他的新娘</p>\n<p>在一阵蓝色的火焰中来到海边</p>\n<p>跟一个女孩说</p>\n<p>  “芥麦花的花语是恋人”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235607419.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235607419\"></p>\n<p>那个孤单的神</p>\n<p>在无数人的人生里驻足停留</p>\n<p>终于有人给了他一个答案</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235617159.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235617159\"></p>\n<p>因为遇见她人生无与伦比</p>\n<p>因为遇见”她每一时刻都很璀璨</p>\n<p>因为遇见她<br>“天气好，天气不好，天气刚刚好，每一天都很美好”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235626443.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235626443\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235631026.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235631026\"></p>\n<p>所以他祈求神明，在天气刚好的一天让他告白吧</p>\n<p>即便是化为虚无化为风和雪</p>\n<p>在白色沙漠里数着自己的脚印行走好多年</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235637857.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235637857\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235642988.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235642988\"></p>\n<p>“或许你是我的命运，于是你降临了”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235650038.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235650038\"></p>\n<p>  东门烤红薯糖炒栗子的香气提醒了我：“又到了看鬼怪的季节啊～”</p>\n<p>  刚好这段时间“心软的神”这个梗被提起，我们突发灵感，和潇哥约着在学校里拍一组日落光氛围感夜景写真。</p>\n<p>  成都的秋雨天果然没让我们“失望”。拍摄时间选在了飘着小雨的傍晚，潇哥穿着黑大衣撑着黑伞，我们笑道“潇哥，来都来了，拍一个心软的神吧？”于是便有了开头的视频（潇哥抖音指路：严一）</p>\n<p>  《stay with me》是鬼怪里我最喜欢的ost之一，旋律响起时仿佛还能看到鬼怪和他的新娘在初雪时的告白。</p>\n<p> 这么说着，我已经开始期待成都今年的初雪了～</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303235703875.png\" alt=\"image-20220303235703875\"></p>\n<p>祝大家能在这个冬天遇到命定之人</p>\n<p>我们下次再见~</p>\n<p>:::details 感谢</p>\n<p>摄影｜李宜霏 杨钰涵 </p>\n<p>摄像｜徐皓辰 刘雨童</p>\n<p>模特｜严一潇</p>\n<p>文｜刘雨童</p>\n<p>排版｜杨钰涵</p>\n<p>:::details</p>\n","text":"“See ya never gone my way Better will someday” 我们见一面吧 在冬天，在下雪天 在我们最浪漫的年纪里 他出现在飘落的初雪里 因为她的召唤 因为她在等待 所以会在寒冬有了樱花飘落和22℃的灿烂阳光 他会站在芥麦花田里拿着一束花等待他的新...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":701,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":7,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"冬","slug":"冬","count":2,"path":"api/tags/冬.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-2022030323474